<section class="m-header-static">
  <div class="inner">
    <header>
      <h2>Contribute data to Global Forest Watch</h2>
      <h3>Would you like to publish your data to the <a href="/map">GFW Interactive Map</a>? Just complete this form!</h3>
      <p>NOTE: Although the GFW team will make every effort to add all data submitted via this form, there may be instances where GFW does not support the type or format of data. We will contact you if we are unable to add your data to GFW.</p>
    </header>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="m-section-static" id="contributeDataView">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="m-new -no-aside">
      <!-- <aside class="m-aside">
        <h3>HOW TO CREATE YOUR SUBSCRIPTIONS</h3>

        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Mauris faucibus dolor a suscipit tincidunt. Ut sagittis porta nunc, nec pellentesque dolor ornare ut. Sed vitae.</p>

